OL,3,CBaby cows bring joy to hospice patients
OL,5,FResidents of a hospice in Chesterfield
OL,6,Fhave been visited by baby cows in an
OL,7,Finitiative to improve their wellbeing.
OL,9,FThe four-week-old brown Swiss calves,
OL,10,Fcalled Bonnie and Bella, were taken to
OL,11,FAshgate Hospice by local farmer Rob
OL,12,FPearson and his partner Emma Brookbank.
OL,14,FMr Pearson, 54, a long-time supporter
OL,15,Fof the hospice, said he wanted to
OL,16,Fstart giving back after his mother and
OL,17,Fniece received end-of-life care at the
OL,18,Fhospice.
