OL,3,CBaby cows bring joy to hospice patients
OL,5,FHe said: "I lost my mum in 2012, and
OL,6,Fthe hospice were very good with caring
OL,7,Ffor her. Plus you never know if you'll
OL,8,Fneed the care yourself one day.
OL,10,F"You only have to see the look on the
OL,11,Fpatients faces when we bring in the
OL,12,Fanimals ` that makes the whole thing
OL,13,Fworth it."
OL,15,FThe cows visited the hospice's
OL,16,Finpatient unit and day services
OL,17,Fpatients and their families.
OL,19,FAmong the patients who met the baby
OL,20,Fcows was Carol Harland, 75, from
OL,21,FBakewell.
