OL,3,CBaby cows bring joy to hospice patients
OL,5,FShe said: "The cows have been
OL,6,Fgorgeous."
OL,8,FAnother patient, Mary Elaine Thompson,
OL,9,F72, who was admitted to the IPU two
OL,10,Fweeks ago, after being diagnosed with
OL,11,Fcancer, said: "They are fabulous. What
OL,12,Fa place this is!"
OL,14,FThe hospice has welcomed various
OL,15,Fanimals in the past.
OL,17,FPaula Cockayne, Ward Sister, at
OL,18,FAshgate Hospice said: "We are really
OL,19,Fgrateful for our community supporters
OL,20,Fwho come and do these lovely things."
