OL,3,CBaby cows bring joy to hospice patients
OL,5,F"It gives the patients a bit of a
OL,6,Fdistraction from a very challenging
OL,7,Ftimes in their lives.
OL,9,F"We've had a pony, we've had lambs
OL,10,Fwe've had guinea pigs. We always
OL,11,Fencourage animals to come such as
OL,12,Ffamily pets."
OL,14,FMr Pearson hopes to continue bringing
OL,15,Fanimals to visit the patients at the
OL,16,Fhospice however, admitted that some
OL,17,Fanimals might not be the best visitors
OL,19,F"I have been asked to bring some
OL,20,Fpiglets down which would be
OL,21,Fdisastrous," he said.
